animeDescription: Hiroe Ogawa is a healthy, normal girl with an extraordinary, private dilemma. Hiroe is unable to reach sexual climax under any circumstances. Over Hiroe's objections, older housemate Mayaka and landlady Yayoi use a varity of sexual techniques, appendages, and even hypnotism in order to help Hiroe achieve her elusive goal.(Source: ANN)
animeCharacters: ['Ogawa, Hiroe', 'Scientist', 'Fortune Teller', "Takami's Friend 1", 'Ogawa, Mayaka', 'Hiroe (Possessed)', 'Oide, Takami', 'Yayoi', "Takami's Friend 2", 'Sumio']
